<section id="bio">
    <h2>Professional Bio</h2>
    <p>
        Davie Webb is a specialist start-up and scale-up product leader with over 12 years of experience in user-focused web app and SaaS solutions. He excels in uniting cross-functional teams for impactful product delivery, both strategically and tactically. In July 2022, Davie launched his consultancy, Dawn Chorus Digital, working on high-profile transformation projects.
        His notable achievements include pioneering Boomin.com, a disruptive start-up that attracted over 1 million monthly site visits, and revolutionizing the customer experience at Purplebricks, creating the largest estate agency in the UK.
        Davie is passionate about AI-powered products and continually looks to leverage AI throughout the product lifecycle.
    </p>
</section>

